{"tid":1328362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲議會將辯論香港議案　促控出口免港獲侵犯權利科技","createTime":"2019-07-18T01:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T01:58:03.000Z","uid":48973,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85d2ef78c0b17f5a299e656a285a4252126f1a8b","tid":1328362,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:45:45.000Z","msg":"歐洲議會將於周四（18日）早上辯論香港現況，決議案議題包括促請港府撤回修訂《逃犯條例》、釋放及不檢控和平示威者、就警察對示威者使用的武力進行獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n決議案原提及要求歐盟對外事務部禁止出口群眾控制裝備，以及「非致命」武器，其後多個黨團提出聯合動議，字眼上改為促請歐盟的成員國及國際社會實施適當的出口控制，以<span style=\"color: red;\">拒絕中國、香港獲得可以侵犯基本權利的科技</span>。<br />\n<br />\n除了反修例風波，決議案議題亦包括譴責中國持續增加干預香港內部事務，尤其中方近日稱《中英聯合聲明》為不再有效的歷史文件，促請中央按聯合聲明維持香港的高度自治、權利及自由。決議案亦關注新聞自由，稱香港記者受到前所未有壓力，尤其是報道內地敏感議題時，自我審查有所增加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190718/s00001/1563407944579/%e6%ad%90%e6%b4%b2%e8%ad%b0%e6%9c%83%e5%b0%87%e8%be%af%e8%ab%96%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%ad%b0%e6%a1%88-%e4%bf%83%e6%8e%a7%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e5%85%8d%e6%b8%af%e7%8d%b2%e4%be%b5%e7%8a%af%e6%ac%8a%e5%88%a9%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190718%2Fs00001%2F1563407944579%2F%25e6%25ad%2590%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25b0%2587%25e8%25be%25af%25e8%25ab%2596%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e6%25a1%2588-%25e4%25bf%2583%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%258f%25a3%25e5%2585%258d%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%258d%25b2%25e4%25be%25b5%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25ac%258a%25e5%2588%25a9%25e7%25a7%2591%25e6%258a%2580&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakvrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=bca45fd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190718%2Fs00001%2F1563407944579%2F%25e6%25ad%2590%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25b0%2587%25e8%25be%25af%25e8%25ab%2596%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e6%25a1%2588-%25e4%25bf%2583%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%258f%25a3%25e5%2585%258d%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%258d%25b2%25e4%25be%25b5%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25ac%258a%25e5%2588%25a9%25e7%25a7%2591%25e6%258a%2580&h=77e1a297\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190718/s00001/1563407944579/%e6%ad%90%e6%b4%b2%e8%ad%b0%e6%9c%83%e5%b0%87%e8%be%af%e8%ab%96%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%ad%b0%e6%a1%88-%e4%bf%83%e6%8e%a7%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e5%85%8d%e6%b8%af%e7%8d%b2%e4%be%b5%e7%8a%af%e6%ac%8a%e5%88%a9%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80</a>"},{"pid":"f59185f07d28bb6431801bdbfba8453bec690d22","tid":1328362,"uid":48973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:51:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e0dcadfbfc5672a7f526fd17f1e6f2017905eca8","tid":1328362,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:53:20.000Z","msg":"紅字係指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9a839388ed420a5f60d94d7f9f41f71faebebd","tid":1328362,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0dcadfbfc5672a7f526fd17f1e6f2017905eca8","tid":1328362,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:53:20.000Z","msg":"紅字係指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd6277e4bcb5f7efab0f512c7672539a62c1911","tid":1328362,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:58:03.000Z","msg":"「譴責中國持續增加干預香港內部事務」<br />\n串番中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}